Revision history for POE-Component-IRC-Plugin-BasePoCoWrap

0.007   2013-11-11
        - Minor fixes to comply with specs and Kwalitee game   

0.006   2010-02-27
        - Added `response_types`; changed _send_event() to send_event()

0.005   2008-11-01
        - Added ability to return a string from _make_response_message()
          instead of always having to return an arrayref

0.004   2008-08-08
        - Fixed the bug which prevented creating plugins that
          required no input.

0.003   2008-07-31
        - Fixed documentation a bit. Added separate triggers support
          as well as the _message_into_response_event() method

0.002   2008-03-10
        - Added 'root' functionality and fixed up the
          PLUGIN DOCUMENTATION section a bit.

0.001   2008-03-09
        - First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

